article_text:
New York

Walk Score: 87.6

The real estate site Walk Score wants you to live in a vibrant, walkable city where you can enjoy the culture and excitement of a rich street life. Their Walk Scores are ranked from zero to 100. No surprise to the NY office of TFT, New York ranks number one. Recommended: Little Italy, Chinatown, NoHo, and the new World Trade Center.
